<references />

===Usage notes===
an old-fashioned term that was primarily used to describe non-[[w:Hoklo people|Hoklo people]] from Mainland China, a large number of whom had emmigrated to Taiwan after 1949.  This term later came to be replaced by [[gōa-séng-lâng]] ([[外省人]]).

